Steps to update timezone in CentOS are as follows:

1) Run the following command to check the present time zone

    ls -l /etc/localtime

2) Search the timezone you want to set using the following command

    timedatectl list-timezones | grep "time_zone" where time_zone is desired one to be set

3) Set timezone using the following command

    timedatectl set-timezone "time_zone" where time_zone is desired one to be set

4) After this, please execute ls -l /etc/localtime to check timezone after change.
